{
  "id": "62088471f001b5001f7d1e55",
  "title": "おじさん構文",
  "created": 1644725380,
  "updated": 1775481007,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "62088471f001b5001f7d1e55",
      "text": "おじさん構文",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1644725380,
      "updated": 1644725380
    },
    {
      "id": "69c91cf1000000000022fa68",
      "text": " [おじさん]が書く独特の気持ち悪い文章のこと",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774787826,
      "updated": 1774787826
    },
    {
      "id": "620884855b98c20000c8d4dc",
      "text": " [https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E3%81%8A%E3%81%98%E3%81%95%E3%82%93%E6%A7%8B%E6%96%87 おじさん構文 - Wikipedia]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1644725381,
      "updated": 1774787826
    },
    {
      "id": "6208a85f7838e30000c85c5d",
      "text": " おじさん構文で文章を生成する「[おじさん文章ジェネレーター]」なるものも存在する",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1644734560,
      "updated": 1774787822
    },
    {
      "id": "69c91cb7000000000022fa66",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774787768,
      "updated": 1774787768
    },
    {
      "id": "6208a8607838e30000c85c5e",
      "text": "[ojichat]",
      "userId": "6273cf7adf39ca001db9fdff",
      "created": 1644734560,
      "updated": 1652353716
    },
    {
      "id": "627ceaa9b9fdff00003d422f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6273cf7adf39ca001db9fdff",
      "created": 1652353714,
      "updated": 1652353714
    },
    {
      "id": "63abe16ee60035000004b6be",
      "text": ">[https://twitter.com/yokoi_bitko/status/1607375232335241227 @yokoi_bitko]: 1日3回 [怪文書]が届くようになった[ミオミオ]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1672208750,
      "updated": 1672208764
    },
    {
      "id": "63abe172e60035000004b6c0",
      "text": ">#水星の魔女",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1672208754,
      "updated": 1672208754
    },
    {
      "id": "63abe172e60035000004b6c1",
      "text": ">[https://gyazo.com/8a08bf595a785cae16d0d11743df9280]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1672208754,
      "updated": 1688774437
    },
    {
      "id": "63abe172e60035000004b6c2",
      "text": "　1期終わった後に見直すと味わい深い",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1672208754,
      "updated": 1675224030
    },
    {
      "id": "684137fa00000000006057ff",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1749104635,
      "updated": 1749104635
    },
    {
      "id": "684137fb0000000000605800",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1749104635,
      "updated": 1749104635
    },
    {
      "id": "684137fb0000000000605801",
      "text": "[GPT.icon]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1749104636,
      "updated": 1749104636
    },
    {
      "id": "684137fb0000000000605802",
      "text": "[* オジサン構文の例]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1749104636,
      "updated": 1749104636
    },
    {
      "id": "684137fb0000000000605803",
      "text": "  こんにちは！今日は晴れてて気持ちいいネ☀️✨",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1749104636,
      "updated": 1749104636
    },
    {
      "id": "684137fb0000000000605804",
      "text": "  みんな元気かな？最近は寒くなってきたから、風邪ひかないように気をつけてね💪😊",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1749104636,
      "updated": 1749104636
    },
    {
      "id": "684137fb0000000000605805",
      "text": "  あ、そういえば昨日は美味しいラーメンを食べたヨ🍜💕",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1749104636,
      "updated": 1749104636
    },
    {
      "id": "684137fb0000000000605806",
      "text": "  ここのお店は最高なんだ！チャーシューがトロトロで、スープも絶品だったヨ〜✨",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1749104636,
      "updated": 1749104636
    },
    {
      "id": "684137fb0000000000605808",
      "text": "  それと、最近は趣味でガーデニングを始めたンダ🌼🌿",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1749104636,
      "updated": 1749104636
    },
    {
      "id": "684137fb0000000000605809",
      "text": "  お花が咲くのを見ると、心が癒されるネ〜😌💖",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1749104636,
      "updated": 1749104636
    },
    {
      "id": "684137fb000000000060580a",
      "text": "  みんなも何か新しいこと始めてみると、楽しいかもよ👍😄",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1749104636,
      "updated": 1749104636
    },
    {
      "id": "684137fb000000000060580c",
      "text": "  じゃあ、またね〜！良い一日を送ってネ😊🌈",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1749104636,
      "updated": 1749104636
    },
    {
      "id": "63d9e3b85e90c000008ca413",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675223992,
      "updated": 1675223992
    },
    {
      "id": "684ab4c8000000000034361d",
      "text": "[nyarla.icon]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1749726408,
      "updated": 1749726411
    },
    {
      "id": "684ab4cb000000000034361f",
      "text": "\t[Misskey]などで[カスタム絵文字]を多用することがオジサン構文である可能性を指摘されている[要出典]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1749726411,
      "updated": 1749726500
    },
    {
      "id": "684ab4c9000000000034361e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1749726409,
      "updated": 1749726409
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3a653000000000088d42a",
      "text": "おじさん構文を狙った作文はインターネットで見つかるけど、現実のやり取りで自然に起きたおじさん構文を見たことがない[vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775478356,
      "updated": 1775481007
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3a656000000000088d42b",
      "text": "\tLINEとか個人間のやり取りで出てくる印象[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775478359,
      "updated": 1775478443
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3a656000000000088d42c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775478359,
      "updated": 1775478359
    },
    {
      "id": "69c91b42000000000022fa5a",
      "text": "特徴を使った例文を作成したり、",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774787394,
      "updated": 1774787451
    },
    {
      "id": "69c91b4e000000000022fa5d",
      "text": "文章をおじさん構文に書き換えると習熟できる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774787407,
      "updated": 1774787440
    },
    {
      "id": "69c91b42000000000022fa5b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774787394,
      "updated": 1774787394
    },
    {
      "id": "69c90d7100000000009a49c6",
      "text": "文で示されている情報に重ねて絵文字で表す",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774783858,
      "updated": 1774783924
    },
    {
      "id": "69c90d7e00000000009a49c8",
      "text": " 野球⚾️をしました",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774783871,
      "updated": 1774783881
    },
    {
      "id": "69c90d8400000000009a49c9",
      "text": " 病院🏥に行きました",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774783877,
      "updated": 1774783895
    },
    {
      "id": "69c90d9600000000009a49ca",
      "text": "文中の情報を絵文字に置き換える",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774783895,
      "updated": 1774783904
    },
    {
      "id": "69c90da000000000009a49cb",
      "text": " ⚾️をしました",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774783904,
      "updated": 1774791595
    },
    {
      "id": "69c90da700000000009a49cc",
      "text": " 🏥に行きました",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774783911,
      "updated": 1774783911
    },
    {
      "id": "69c92b8e0000000000b63c53",
      "text": " 🍰を食べました",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774791566,
      "updated": 1774791590
    },
    {
      "id": "69c90da700000000009a49cd",
      "text": "絵文字で情報を加える",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774783912,
      "updated": 1774786096
    },
    {
      "id": "69c90dca00000000009a49cf",
      "text": " 先輩⚾️は何て言ってました？",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774783947,
      "updated": 1774786103
    },
    {
      "id": "69c90dd600000000009a49d0",
      "text": "  野球ボールの絵文字で先輩(とくに野球部の先輩)だと表してる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774783959,
      "updated": 1774786087
    },
    {
      "id": "69c90d7100000000009a49c7",
      "text": "一部の記号を使う",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774783858,
      "updated": 1774787727
    },
    {
      "id": "69c91c57000000000022fa61",
      "text": " ‼️赤いビックリマーク",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774787672,
      "updated": 1774787711
    },
    {
      "id": "69c91c67000000000022fa62",
      "text": " 💦汗",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774787688,
      "updated": 1774787691
    },
    {
      "id": "69c91c6b000000000022fa63",
      "text": "絵文字が多い",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774787691,
      "updated": 1774787734
    },
    {
      "id": "69c91c97000000000022fa65",
      "text": "寒い感じ",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774787735,
      "updated": 1774788819
    },
    {
      "id": "69c9162900000000009a49d1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774786089,
      "updated": 1774786089
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3a615000000000088d40a",
      "text": "会話で他人が悪口を使うと嫌だな、避けたいなと思うのに、おじさん構文を知ったときには抵抗なく受け入れて見下した[vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775478293,
      "updated": 1775478481
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3a615000000000088d40c",
      "text": " なんでだ",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775478293,
      "updated": 1775478293
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3a615000000000088d40d",
      "text": " こういうのを避けたい",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775478293,
      "updated": 1775478293
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3a615000000000088d40e",
      "text": " 笑われてる淫夢を見て笑う",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775478293,
      "updated": 1775478299
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3a615000000000088d40b",
      "text": "\t避けたいと思っているほど逆にずっとそのことが付き纏ってくる（同じことが起こるたびに嫌になる）[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775478293,
      "updated": 1775478539
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3a70c0000000000313503",
      "text": "\t\t逆に自分でやってみると良き。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775478540,
      "updated": 1775478632
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3a7670000000000313504",
      "text": "\t\t「やっちゃダメなこと」という意識から開放されて他人がやっていても今ほど強く嫌には思わなくなる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775478632,
      "updated": 1775478632
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3a6d50000000000313502",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775478486,
      "updated": 1775478486
    },
    {
      "id": "684a05ca0000000000723d2d",
      "text": "[おばさん構文]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1749681610,
      "updated": 1775478486
    },
    {
      "id": "684a05cb0000000000723d2e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1749681612,
      "updated": 1749681612
    }
  ]
}